Proyecto EmbedIA
All rights reserved.

Project description:
EmbedIA is a framework that transforms neural network models developed
in Python (e.g., with TensorFlow/Keras) and algorithms from the
Scikit-learn library, for efficient implementation on microcontrollers
and embedded systems.

